OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with patchy rain north
OL,6,Fat first then outbreaks of locally
OL,7,Fheavy rain in the south soon spreads
OL,8,Fnortheast. This rain will clear to
OL,9,Fbright spells and scattered showers in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright or clear spells with
OL,13,Fshowery rain at first becoming cloudy
OL,14,Fwith outbreaks of rain, some heavy,
OL,15,Ffrom just after midnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy rain becoming drier
OL,19,Fwith bright spells from the mid-
OL,20,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
